- set_meta_tags title: 'Business Plan Assistance', description: 'Achieve business growth with an effective business plan. Excide helps  with market analysis, organization management, marketing, sales, funding, financial projections.', reverse: true
section.text-center.imagebg.space--lg data-overlay="3"
  .background-image-holder
    = image_pack_tag "media/src/images/business-plan-assistance.jpeg", alt: "image", class: 'background-image'
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-8.col-lg-12
        h1.type-uppercase Business Plan Assistance
        h4 Assisting you in planning your business ventures
        ol.breadcrumbs
          li
            a href="/"  Home
          li
            a href="/financial-analytics-reporting/"  Virtual Financial Officer
          li Business Plan Assistance
section
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-sm-12
        .text-center
          h3.mb-5.type--uppercase Every business needs a business plan
        p.lead.m32.pb32 Every business needs a business plan. It is the first essential step to take before entering the business. Many entrepreneurs start out with a brilliant idea but with a badly planned business structure, their business fail due to bad execution and poor business planning.
        p.lead.m32 Business plans are strategic and is important for businesses. By planning out a detailed business strategy, you will be able to have a better idea how you are going to handle your business in both short term and long term. This plan will be able to determine what actions you are going to take when your business becomes more established in the future.
section.pt240.pb240.imagebg.height-30
  .background-image-holder
    = image_pack_tag "media/src/images/pen-on-notebook.jpg", alt: "image", class: 'background-image'
section
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-sm-12
        .text-center
          h3.mb-5.type--uppercase Why Excide?
        p.lead.m32 At Excide, we help structure a business plan pertaining to your business model and ideas. We will help you uncover what are the necessary steps to take in order to make your business flourish. By answering some questions such as:

        ul.lead data-bullet="ti-check-box"
          li Executive Summary
          li Company Description
          li Market Analysis
          li Organization & Management
          li Service or Product Line
          li Marketing & Sales
          li Funding Request
          li Financial Projections
          li How to Make Your Business Plan Stand Out

        p.lead.m32.pb32 We will be able to help provide you detailed steps to take to ensure that your business take flight under our guidance. We will also provide you with our own financial model for your reference to aid you in your finances on a regular basis.
section.imagebg.overlay
  .background-image-holder
    = image_pack_tag "media/src/images/table-top-post-its.jpg", alt: "image", class: 'background-image'
  .container
    .row
      .col-sm-12.text-center
        h3.type--uppercase.mb-5.mb-xs-32 More Services
        = render 'services_list'
section#contactus
  .container
    .row.mb--2
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-sm-12.text-center
        h4.mb-5.type--uppercase Need to know more about what we offer?
        p.lead.mb-5 There is nothing like a face-to-face meeting to better understand each other. Leave your details below and we will get in touch with you soon.
    = render 'contact'